long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export TikTok accounts data from the accounts search page to a XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open a TikTok accounts search page.
2️⃣ Click the Download button next to the search tab.     
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in tiktok accounts search page.
2️⃣ Running solely on your local machine, no need to worry about any privacy concerns, all data remains on your local device.
3️⃣ Export accounts data to a xls/csv file, data include: uid, custom_verify, follow_status, follower_count, nickname, unique_id, signature, user_url, avatar_thumb, originSearchUrl.

✨ Why use this:
✨ Conduct sentiment analysis and find authentic product reviews
👩‍🔬 Obtain data for research and social listening experiments
🦠 Analyze trends, viral campaigns and content of specific creators
🥸 Identify unverified content and inaccurate information with high public value
📚 Prepare for or analyze a TikTok marketing campaign

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by TikTok❗️🔒
